SN55: Precog.description: Precog, Subnet #55 of Bittensor launched by Coin Metrics in collaboration with Yuma, is revolutionizing crypto-asset price forecasting. Leveraging decentralized AI and premium data, Precog generates precise Bitcoin price predictions every five minutes, setting a new standard for financial intelligence in digital markets. This innovative subnetwork embodies the power of collaboration and machine learning within the Bittensor ecosystem.
